title: Dillard’s, Inc. to Report First Quarter Results
text:
LITTLE ROCK, Ark.--(BUSINESS WIRE)-- Dillard’s, Inc. (NYSE: DDS) will announce results for the 13 weeks ended May 5, 2018 tomorrow, May 17, 2018, before the opening of the New York Stock Exchange.
